;;; Commentary:

;; Jump to line number at point.
:; Back to position before the jump.
;;

;;; Examples of jump:

;; /path/to/a.txt:5 ; Jump to /path/to/a.txt, line 5 (Ruby style)
;; ../a.txt:5       ; Relative path
;; a.txt            ; Only filename
;; a.txt(1,2)       ; C# style
;; a.txt, line 1    ; Python
;; a.txt line 1     ; Perl

